<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>About Us | MeetTheMakers</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
        }
      
        .about-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background: white;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .about-section h1 {
            color: #ff6600;
        }
        .row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .col-2 {
            width: 45%;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f8f8;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
 

    </style>
</head>
<body>
   <%-include('./partials/navbar')%>
    <div class="about-section">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>
            At <strong>MeetTheMakers</strong>, we believe in the power of creativity and innovation. Our platform serves as a bridge, connecting talented makers with passionate buyers who value unique, handmade creations.
        </p>
        <p>
            Founded with the mission to support creators and nurture entrepreneurship, MeetTheMakers celebrates craftsmanship and the individuals behind each masterpiece.
        </p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-2">
                <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                <p>To create a global hub where creativity meets opportunity, empowering makers to thrive in a supportive and dynamic marketplace.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-2">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>To provide an inclusive platform that nurtures creativity, promotes craftsmanship, and connects makers with enthusiasts who appreciate handmade goods.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%-include('./partials/footer') %>
 
</body>
</html>